    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates adequate credibility for identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index predictions validated against FDA benchmark data with quantified uncertainty. The methodology described in the hemolysis model calibration study (referenced via referencesIdentifier) provides the theoretical basis for the power-law exponent values adopted in this assessment. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. Decision: model is fit for purpose for the stated COU.",
